<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Categories - StoryLoom</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    {{> header}}

    <main class="container">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h1>Categories</h1>
            <p>These categories combine traditional bookstore classifications with specialized thematic reading lists, automatically assigned based on the archival focus.</p>

            <div class="category-columns">
                
